    <div class="bg-info blurb"><strong><i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i> Alpha</strong> <p>We are currently in public alpha, which means things may not work perfectly – yet. If you encounter something that looks broken, please let us know!</p></div>
    <hr>
    <div class="well">
        <a href="mailto:yosriady@gmail.com" class="btn btn-block btn-default"><i class="fa fa-paper-plane-o"></i> Contact Us</a>
    </div>
    <div class="panel panel-default">
        <%= render 'layouts/twitter_widget' %>
        <%= render 'layouts/facebook_widget' %>
    </div>

</div>

</div>

